        <h2 class="artical-title">What Are Lab-Grown Diamonds? Are They Real?</h2>
        <p>To put it very simply, a lab-grown diamond is a diamond that is grown in a laboratory. Many people wonder whether something that is grown in a lab can be considered a real diamond. The short answer is, yes! Lab-grown diamonds are real diamonds. In fact, they have the same chemical and physical composition as mined diamonds. But, we totally get that you need more than just our word. To help you understand why lab-grown diamonds are the real deal, let’s take a look at how they are created.
        </p>
